bb2mdir
=======

Short description
-----------------

`bb2mdir` download web pages from an internet forum, and outputs emails
messages that you can open with your favorite Mail User Agent.

Current status
--------------

At the moment, bb2mdir only works with [punbb](http://punbb.informer.com/), and
it is probably not ready enough for use yet. But your help is most welcome !

Implementation
--------------

It is written in Python, and uses BeautifulSoup for parsing.
